components.name: AppControlsComponent
components.templateData:
<mat-card class="mat-elevation-z0 box">
  <mat-card-header>
    <mat-card-title class="pb-5">All Controls</mat-card-title>
  </mat-card-header>
  <mat-card-content>
    <app-text-control
      [formControlModel]="appControls.textField"
      [form]="form"
      (iconClick)="onIconClick(input)"
      #input
    ></app-text-control
  ></mat-card-content>
  <mat-card-content>
    <app-text-control-number
      [formControlModel]="appControls.numberField"
      [form]="form"
    >
    </app-text-control-number>
  </mat-card-content>
  <mat-card-content>
    <app-select
      [formControlModel]="appControls.selectField"
      [form]="form"
      [options]="selectOptions"
    ></app-select>
  </mat-card-content>
  <mat-card-content>
    <app-multi-chip-select
      [formControlModel]="appControls.multiChipSelectField"
      [formControl]="getSelectionControl('multiChipSelectField')"
      [form]="form"
      [allItems]="multiChipSelect"
      ngDefaultControl
    ></app-multi-chip-select>
  </mat-card-content>

  <mat-card-content>
    <app-time-picker
      (timeChanged)="onTimeChange($event)"
      [timePickerModel]="appControls.timePickerField"
      [form]="form"
    ></app-time-picker>
  </mat-card-content>
  <mat-card-content>
    <app-toggle
      [form]="form"
      [formControlModel]="appControls.toggleField"
    ></app-toggle>
  </mat-card-content>
  <mat-card-content>
    <app-radio
      [formControlModel]="appControls.radioField"
      [form]="form"
      [options]="radioOptions"
    ></app-radio>
  </mat-card-content>
  <mat-card-content>
    <app-checkbox
      [formControlModel]="appControls.checkboxField"
      [form]="form"
    ></app-checkbox>
  </mat-card-content>
  <mat-card-content>
    <app-file-upload
      [formControlModel]="appControls.fileUploadField"
      [form]="form"
    >
    </app-file-upload>
  </mat-card-content>
  <mat-card-content>
    <app-date-picker
    [form]="form"
    [formControlModel]="appControls.datePickerField"
  ></app-date-picker>
  </mat-card-content>
  <mat-card-content>
    <app-button
      type="button"
      label="Button Control"
      (btnClick)="submit()"
    ></app-button>
  </mat-card-content>
  <mat-card-content>
    <app-stroked-button      
      label="Stroked Button Control"
      (onBtnClick)="submit()"
    ></app-stroked-button>
  </mat-card-content>
</mat-card>

components.name: MultiChipSelectComponent
components.templateData:
<mat-form-field class="form-field" [formGroup]="form">
  <mat-chip-list #chipList>
    <mat-chip
      *ngFor="let item of getSelectedItems()"
      [selectable]="selectable"
      [removable]="removable"
      (removed)="remove(item)"
    >
      {{ item.label }}
      <mat-icon matChipRemove *ngIf="removable">cancel</mat-icon>
    </mat-chip>
    <input
      [placeholder]="formControlModel.label"
      [name]="formControlModel.key"
      #input
      (click)="onClickSelect()"
      [formControl]="fieldCtrl"
      [matAutocomplete]="auto"
      [matChipInputFor]="chipList"
      [matChipInputSeparatorKeyCodes]="separatorKeysCodes"
      [matChipInputAddOnBlur]="addOnBlur"
      (matChipInputTokenEnd)="add($event)"
    />
  </mat-chip-list>
  <mat-autocomplete #auto="matAutocomplete" (optionSelected)="selected($event)">
    <mat-option
      *ngFor="let item of filteredItems | async"
      [value]="item"
      [disabled]="isOptionDisabled(item)"
    >
      {{ item.label }}
    </mat-option>
  </mat-autocomplete>
</mat-form-field>
